Disk World creator help
close_case

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
close_case -  This method closes the case.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int close_case(string area,
int id,
string closer,
string result,
mixed data)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area the case is in
%^BOLD%^id%^RESET%^ - the id of the case to close
%^BOLD%^closer%^RESET%^ - the person that closes the case
%^BOLD%^result%^RESET%^ - the string saying what the result of the case is
%^BOLD%^desc%^RESET%^ - the description of the close reason
%^BOLD%^data%^RESET%^ - special internal data used specifically for appeals
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/inherit/case_control.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method closes the case.
.EP

